</caption>
</subSubSection>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="162" pageNumber="765" type="description">
<paragraph blockId="162.[92,1297,2942,3483]" pageId="162" pageNumber="765">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[93,346,2981,3010]" pageId="162" pageNumber="765">Descriptive notes.</emphasis>
No external measurements available. This species’ fur is reddish brown to rusty above, with grayflanks and sharply demarcated white belly. Lips and cheeks are white; there is no subauricular tuft. Tail is dark, nearly blackish throughout, with no terminal tuft, and presumably is very long and semi-prehensile. Feet are whitish dorsally.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
